chalow is an (Emacs) ChangeLog to HTML converter

Quick usage:

    cd /path/to/chalow-directory
    perl chalow --name "Title of the ChangeLog" --descr "Description of the ChangeLog" -c cl.en.conf /path/to/ChangeLog -o /path/to/output-directory
    cp sample/diary.css /path/to/output-directory

cl.conf is the original Japanese configuration file.

cl.en.conf is an English variant and cl.de.conf a German variant.
